      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>In ''The Hunt'' on April 22, an apartment hunter laments that he was not aware of buyers' brokers in the Bronx. Since February 2006, we have been selling prewar co-ops ranging from 550-square-foot studios to 1,500-square-foot three-bedroom, two-bath apartments.</p>
        <p>A steadily growing migration of Manhattanites and out-of-state parents buying for children are now in the area surrounding Yankee Stadium. At prices from $75,000 to $395,000, we've sold 16 units, with two in contract.</p>
        <p>Ariela Heilman  Ariela Heilman Real Estate  Manhattan</p>
      </block>
